    "The complete ChatGPT chat log from this training session is also available as supplementary material for further reference.",
    "The final intervention, conducted on the twelfth week during the third activity session, students were challenged to create a Spanish-English dictionary program.",
    "The targeted topics were lists, strings, and file input and output.",
    "Similarly, students were allowed to use ChatGPT but with an additional layer of support.",
    "In particular, the lab instructions document included prompt examples under each sub-task, providing students with clear guidance on how to effectively interact with ChatGPT to receive the appropriate assistance."
